OL,3,C'Site safety' worker 'avoided being
OL,4,Chit by train by two seconds' in near
OL,5,Cmiss
OL,7,FA railway track worker in charge of
OL,8,Fsafety narrowly avoided being hit by a
OL,9,Ftrain travelling at 54mph in Devon.
OL,11,FThe train missed the National Rail
OL,12,Fworker - who was the Controller of
OL,13,FSite Safety - by a matter of seconds.
OL,15,FAn investigation has now been
OL,16,Fcompleted into the 'near miss' on 13
OL,17,FMarch near Littlehempston, just
OL,18,Foutside of Totnes.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
