OL,3,C'Site safety' worker 'avoided being
OL,4,Chit by train by two seconds' in near
OL,5,Cmiss
OL,7,FCCTV images show the worker moving
OL,8,Finto the trees alongside the track -
OL,9,Fclearing the train's path with a mere
OL,10,Ftwo seconds to spare.
OL,12,FThe worker then rejoined their team
OL,13,Fand led them through the area where
OL,14,Fthe incident had just occurred. This
OL,15,Fwas done without the line being
OL,16,Fblocked. No-one challenged the 'person
OL,17,Fin charge' about moving so closely to
OL,18,Fthe live tracks.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
