OL,3,C'Site safety' worker 'avoided being
OL,4,Chit by train by two seconds' in near
OL,5,Cmiss
OL,7,FFollowing the near miss, the worker
OL,8,Fsaid they moved out of the safe area
OL,9,Fto investigate whether the space "was
OL,10,Fwide enough to allow work to be
OL,11,Fundertaken safely".
OL,13,FThey also said that they "did not
OL,14,Fconsider that there had been a near
OL,15,Fmiss".
OL,17,FThe RAIB report revealed communication
OL,18,Fon the day of the incident was
OL,19,Fdifficult.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
